Package: matchr
Title: Fast and Reliable Matching of Images
Version: 0.3
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "David",
           family = "Wachsmuth",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "david.wachsmuth@mcgill.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "http://orcid.org/0000-0001-5689-9527"))
Maintainer: David Wachsmuth <david.wachsmuth@mcgill.ca>
Description: Fast and reliable matching of images. It creates unique image
    signatures using perceptual hashing. This allows large sets of images to be 
    compared to each other to identify image matches. The matching process is 
    insensitive to file format, resolution, or compression.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
